{"tid":1446721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極緊急][召人]一齊同我合力建立黑警資料庫!!","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:42:24.000Z","uid":44331,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b15daa4b2755982ee682a2c4931ed30093cf6d0f","tid":1446721,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"［廣傳ＰＬＳ］<br />\n我係早撈巴。今晚，又有少女被近距離ＨＥＡＤＳＨＯＴ爆眼。<br />\n又有黑警扮無間道捉示威者。<br />\n又有速龍直接係葵芳站射催淚彈。成件事已經離撚晒譜。<br />\n <br />\n我知你同我一樣咁嬲。但大家一定要代悲憤為力量。<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地大概都知我地寫緊黑警濫權報告。<br />\n其中一個重要部份就係影片相片資料庫。</span></ins></strong><br />\n我既中期報告只係ＣＯＶＥＲ去到七月中既事件，七月底到依家仲有大量既片要收集，要睇，要分類，要入ＤＡＴＡ。<br />\n我唔講廢話，如果你黎緊幾星期有大量時間，想參與，想為香港出一分力，請你TG 我：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n工作性質：收集各種黑警懷疑濫權影片／相片。記錄低資料來源，網上連結，時間，地點，再分類，寫簡短既評述黑警犯咩事。<br />\n要求：經驗不拘。但要有ＥＱ，有耐性，唔係狂睇片會睇到眼火爆（我自己睇都睇到好ＤＥＰＲＥＳＳＥＤ）。同埋真係要有時間，投入到去做。如果ＪＯＩＮ左，但結果無郁手，反而會令我地失預算。所以真係有咁既閒情逸致至好舉手。"},{"pid":"e83854f5899321d05a7a289305173ae2ead8dac5","tid":1446721,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b95ab2580cd1fde6e0e0e8c6bddd312eb0bfbc8b","tid":1446721,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28249440b9b457b7675efd5e18042fe722b83cec","tid":1446721,"uid":33543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ50YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=f3cd095f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a>"},{"pid":"b7ebdd9cb306e7352cbd82465d583f7e7da2363b","tid":1446721,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d44c788dd990255b3c3e15e06911c1193309636","tid":1446721,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"借位一用唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔試過都唔知<br />\n原來檢舉可以咁開心！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次緊急召集，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一 (8月12日晚) ！！！</span></span>🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘<br />\n所有人再歸位‼️‼️<br />\n集合3至5萬人,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jffMH3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjffMH3E.png&h=f9c0063d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">檢舉&quot;仇恨言論&quot;！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymYeRW7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymYeRW7.png&h=814e30aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\